# Speed Fitness Gym Manager

## Overview
Speed Fitness is a multi-branch gym management application built with React, TypeScript, and Vite. It provides enterprise-grade infrastructure for managing fitness facilities including member management, check-ins, sales, campaigns, staff, and more.

## Project Structure
- `/components/` - Reusable React components including Layout
- `/pages/` - Page components for different routes (Dashboard, Members, CheckIn, etc.)
- `App.tsx` - Main application with routing configuration
- `AppContext.tsx` - Global state management
- `index.tsx` - Application entry point
- `vite.config.ts` - Vite configuration

## Tech Stack
- React 19 with TypeScript
- Vite 6 for bundling
- React Router DOM for routing
- Recharts for data visualization
- Tailwind CSS (via CDN)
- Google GenAI integration

## Development
- Run `npm run dev` to start the development server on port 5000
- Run `npm run build` to build for production

## Deployment
The app is configured for static deployment. The build output goes to the `dist` directory.
